Map AIM_MAZE_V2
Version 1.0 - Beta

Hello, This is My 3rd Map for the CS:S Game. This is the Version 2 of aim_maze Map.

Features:
* More Challenging Maze
* Cubemaps
* Various Optimizations With Occluders, Nodraws, etc...
* Balanced for Both Terrorists and CTs. (Neither CT or T-Sided.)
* Better Lighting than Version 1.

---PLANNED FEATURES IN VERSION 3---
* Maze Will be More Challenging and Bigger
* Better Bot Navigation

Hope you Enjoy!
